'''''MD&DI''''' is a [[trade magazine]] for the medical device and diagnostic industry published by [[UBM Canon]] ([[Los Angeles]]).<ref>{{cite web |title=MDDI - Medical Device and Diagnostic Industry News |url=http://www.qmed.com/supplier/mddi-medical-device-and-diagnostic-industry-news |website=Qualified Supplier Directory |publisher=QMed |accessdate=22 July 2015}}</ref> It includes [[peer-reviewed]] articles on specific technology issues and overviews of key business, industry, and regulatory topics.<ref>{{cite web |title=MD&DI E-Newsletter |url=http://www.bizreport.com/magazines/mddi_e-newsletter.html |website=BizReport |accessdate=22 July 2015}}</ref> It was established in 1979. In 2009 it had a monthly print circulation of 48,040<ref name=promo>{{cite news |title=Publication Name: Medical Device & Diagnostic Industry |url=http://www.biotechmedia.com/y2001-ed-canon-mddi.html |accessdate=23 July 2015 |publisher=Biotech Media Group |date=2009}}</ref> but is now an online publication with a claimed circulation of 89,000. UBM Canon and the magazine has also sponsored the Medical Design and Manufacturing (MD&D) West Conference & Exposition (formerly the MD&DI West Conference & Expo), a [[medical device]] [[trade show]], since 1978.<ref name="OCCons89">{{cite journal |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=5GAEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA135 |title=Orange County Business News |journal=Orange Coast |author=Gordonsmith, J.A. |volume=15 |issue=1 |year=1989 |page=135 |accessdate=12 March 2016}}</ref>

The magazine sponsored the [[Medical Design Excellence Awards]]<ref name=promo/> and produces a list of 100 Notable People in the Medical Device Industry.<ref>{{cite news |title=100 Notable People in the Medical Device Industry |url=https://www-bsac.eecs.berkeley.edu/frontpagefiles/pisano_100/ |accessdate=22 July 2015 |publisher=Berkeley Sensor & Actuator Center |date=June 2008}}</ref> The term "[[use error]]" was first used in May 1995 in an MD&DI guest editorial, ''The Issue Is 'Use,' Not 'User,' Error,'' by William Hyman.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mddionline.com/article/issue-use-not-user-error |title=The Issue is 'Use,' Not 'User,' Error |work=mddionline.com}}</ref>

